##CPGE_SCRIPT
##ScriptVersion: 1.0
##Written: 2026-05-10
##Scene: SCENE_CREDITS
##Author: LordAries1972
##Description: Credits roll — stop gameplay systems, run scrolling text FX.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Clean up gameplay residue
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
STOP EFFECTS
STOP MOUSE
STOP GAMEPAD

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Fade to black, then fade to credits backdrop image
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Execute FadeToBlack(1.0, 0.0)
Execute FadeToImage(2.0, 1.0)

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Credits scroll on texture layer 1
# StartScrollEffect(textureIndex, direction, speed, tileWidth, tileHeight, delay)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Execute StartScrollEffect(1, ScrollUp, 1, 640, 480, 2.0)

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Audio — soft background during credits
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Execute StartPlaybackThread()
Execute SetGlobalVolume(0.6)

